Syntax: password

Changes your in-game password.  You will be prompted to enter your current
password first (for verification), then to choose and confirm a new one.
Passwords must be at least 5 characters long.

The 'passwd' command is an alternate spelling that does the same thing.

If you forget your password, contact a wizard or immortal for assistance.
They can reset it for you from the admin side.

Recommended practices:
  - Use a password you do not use anywhere else.
  - Change your password if you suspect someone else has learned it.
  - You are responsible for anything that happens with your character.

See also: account
